  "wave_0_per_point": "pp=pp+1;\n\n\n\nva=va*1.069+value1*0.01;\nvb=above(value1,va);\n\n\ndx=(value1*q2*treb)*.01;\ndy=(value2*q2*bass)*0.009;\n\nxx=xx+dx;\nyy=yy+dy;\n\nxx=if(above(xx,1),0,if(below(xx,0),1,xx));\nyy=if(above(yy,1),0,if(below(yy,0),1,yy));\n\ny=yy+value1*0.011;\nx=xx;\n\n\nf2=equal((pp)%2,0);\n//f2=1;\n\n\n\nr=(sin(t2*mid)*.5+.5)*f2+(1-f2)*bass_att*.45;\ng=(tan(t2*treb)*.5+.5)*f2+(1-f2)*treb_att*.4;\nb=(cos(t2*bass)*.5+.5)*f2+(1-f2)*mid_att*.5;\n\na=value1*bass;",
